{"tid":2125964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大校園電視：警方紀錄片《暗夜星辰》未經授權擅用片段　警 400 字回應無提侵權","createTime":"2020-07-26T14:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T15:37:03.000Z","uid":105567,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d16bed2e9016f2260f536bab9a77e057915d91c7","tid":2125964,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"香港警務處與《鳳凰衛視》聯合製作的反修例紀錄片《暗夜星辰》日前首播，影片集中描述警方遇上的危險，而對元朗 721 事件及太子站 831 事件隻字不提。香港大學學生會校園電視今日（26日）發聲明，指控香港警務處及鳳凰衛視未經授權之下，擅自使用該台所拍攝的兩條題為「警方在荃灣示威中開實彈打中一人左胸」片段，對此予以強烈譴責。《立場新聞》及港大校園電視向警方查詢，但長達 400 多字的回覆對偷片事件一字未提，只貼上了一段紀錄片的簡介及製作過程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/campus-11_FkKL2_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcampus-11_FkKL2_1200x0.png&h=2100d56b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87-%E6%9A%97%E5%A4%9C%E6%98%9F%E8%BE%B0-%E6%9C%AA%E7%B6%93%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E6%93%85%E7%94%A8%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%259A%2597%25E5%25A4%259C%25E6%2598%259F%25E8%25BE%25B0-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%2593%2585%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=619bab30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%259A%2597%25E5%25A4%259C%25E6%2598%259F%25E8%25BE%25B0-%25E6%259C%25A